# Chi tiết: Adversaries may use to interact with a remote network share using Server Message Block (SMB). The adversary may then perform actions as the logged-on user.
source IN ("WinEventLog:Microsoft-Windows-PowerShell/Operational", "WinEventLog:PowerShellCore/Operational") Channel IN ("Microsoft-Windows-PowerShell/Operational", "PowerShellCore/Operational") EventCode=4104 EventCode=4104 Channel IN ("Microsoft-Windows-PowerShell/Operational", "PowerShellCore/Operational") ScriptBlockText="*New-PSDrive*" ScriptBlockText="*-psprovider *" ScriptBlockText="*filesystem*" ScriptBlockText="*-root *" ScriptBlockText="*\\\\*" ScriptBlockText="*$*"

# ── Suspicious TCP Tunnel Via PowerShell Script ──
# Mức độ  : Trung bình
